Description: GLEP 42 Gentoo news to static blog converter
 geek42 converts GLEP 42 news item repositories into a static blog with
 RSS/Atom feeds, Markdown exports, and a terminal reader — without
 requiring eselect news.
 .
 Features:
  * Parser for GLEP 42 format 1.0 and 2.0
  * Static site generator with semantic HTML and dark mode
  * RSS 2.0 and Atom 1.0 feed generation
  * Read/unread tracking (equivalent to eselect news read new)
  * News file linter with 15 diagnostic rules
  * Compose/revise commands that open $EDITOR with templates
  * Supports aggregating news from multiple git repositories
